BoutrosLab.plotting.survival 3.0.6 2016-10-26 (Erle Holgersen)
-----------------------------------------------------------------
MINOR UPDATES
* Switched to log-rank test as default statistical method when no events in one or more groups.
* Fixed t-test bug in statistical method logic

BoutrosLab.plotting.survival 3.0.5 2016-07-22 (Erle Holgersen)
-----------------------------------------------------------------
MINOR UPDATE
* Added predefined.p.statistic.type argument to create.km.plot to allow for displaying q-value rather than p-value. The statistic type defaults to 'P', and is passed straight to the display.statistical.result function in BPG.

BoutrosLab.plotting.survival 3.0.4 2016-04-28 (Jennifer Aguiar)
-----------------------------------------------------------------
MINOR UPDATES
* Added risktable.fontsize and key.stats.cex parameters to create.km.plot to allow for adjustment of these fontsizes. Fontsizes default to optimal.risktable.paramters and 1.5, respectively (as these were the original hardcoded fontsizes for these parameters). 
